data.description: Welcome to this beautifully renovated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home that exudes warmth and style. Situated in a quiet neighborhood on a dead-end street, this residence offers an ideal blend of modern amenities and timeless charm.  With Pineville attractions not far, this home boasts an open-concept layout that seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas, providing an inviting space for family gatherings and entertaining guests. A large, dedicated laundry room provides ample space for washing, drying, and additional storage, ensuring household chores are a breeze. In addition to the laundry room, a separate storage shed offers even more space for stowing away seasonal items or creating a workshop. The backyard features a fully fenced-in area so pets can roam without worry. Rest easy knowing your home is equipped with a comprehensive security system, providing an extra layer of peace of mind. The guest bathroom has been thoughtfully updated with a sleek new vanity, replacing the previous pedestal sink, adding both style and functionality. Recent updates include new stove/oven, refrigerator, and new flooring in the bedrooms. In addition, the sewage drains have been recently replaced, ensuring a worry-free living experience for years to come. The sellers are willing to consider leaving the washer and dryer with a reasonable offer, providing added convenience for the new homeowners. This home offers a unique opportunity to own a turnkey property that combines modern convenience with a cozy, welcoming ambiance. Don't miss the chance to make this your dream home. Schedule a viewing today!
